  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (893fc9f 2023-09-12T00:28:57.627748000Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge test\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\n```\r\nfunction test_should_fail_1() public {\r\n    vm.expectRevert();\r\n    revert(\"A\");\r\n\r\n    // execution stops here for some reason\r\n\r\n    revert(\"never reverts and test passes\");\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction test_should_fail_2() public {\r\n    vm.expectRevert();\r\n    revert(\"A\");\r\n\r\n    assertTrue(false, \"test pass despite failed condition\");\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nthis tests **pass**, but they should not. \r\n\r\n```\r\nfoundryup: installed - forge 0.2.0 (893fc9f 2023-09-12T00:28:57.627748000Z)\r\nfoundryup: installed - cast 0.2.0 (893fc9f 2023-09-12T00:28:57.752674000Z)\r\nfoundryup: installed - anvil 0.2.0 (893fc9f 2023-09-12T00:28:57.365492000Z)\r\nfoundryup: installed - chisel 0.2.0 (893fc9f 2023-09-12T00:28:57.495467000Z)\r\n```",
